Capital Markets

Company Overview of Schroder Investment Management Limited



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Schroder Investment Management Limited is a privately owned investment manager. The firm launches and manages equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets. The firm also invests in the alternative markets for its clients. It was founded in 1985 and is based in London, United Kingdom. Schroder Investment Management Limited operates as a subsidiary of Schroders plc.


